1
00:02:19,640 --> 00:02:21,079
You killed my brother.

2
00:02:29,000 --> 00:02:30,460
Want to buy a peace amulet?

3
00:02:31,120 --> 00:02:32,320
I see that today,

4
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,770
you will likely suffer a bloody disaster.

5
00:02:36,000 --> 00:02:37,160
Buy my peace amulet,

6
00:02:38,040 --> 00:02:39,970
and it will keep you safe from harm.

7
00:02:40,320 --> 00:02:41,780
Are you looking down on me?

8
00:02:42,640 --> 00:02:44,100
Forget it if you won't buy.

9
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,010
Cut the crap.

10
00:02:47,280 --> 00:02:49,210
I'm here to avenge the Fourth Boss.

11
00:03:12,240 --> 00:03:13,760
Three souls, heed my command.

12
00:03:13,760 --> 00:03:15,160
Spirits, follow my lead.

13
00:03:25,200 --> 00:03:26,400
This guy knows sorcery.

14
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,260
Kill him first.

15
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,600
Step to the Qian gate,

16
00:03:32,079 --> 00:03:32,740
cold blade,

17
00:03:33,160 --> 00:03:34,079
fatal light.

18
00:03:51,600 --> 00:03:52,120
Monster!

19
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:53,650
I'll fight you to the death!

20
00:04:00,640 --> 00:04:01,100
Master,

21
00:04:01,760 --> 00:04:02,960
I know I was wrong.

22
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:04,400
Let me go.

23
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:07,400
There is much gold and silver in my stronghold.

24
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,660
I'll give it all to you.

25
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:10,640
Aren't you going to avenge your brother?

26
00:04:10,640 --> 00:04:11,880
He pillaged and plundered,

27
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,160
and committed all kinds of evil.

28
00:04:13,160 --> 00:04:15,440
I've long wanted to rid the people of this menace.

29
00:04:15,440 --> 00:04:16,040
Let me go.

30
00:04:16,959 --> 00:04:17,560
I promise,

31
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:19,740
I will never be a bandit again.

32
00:04:23,480 --> 00:04:23,940
Master.

33
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:25,060
Master.

34
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:27,080
Master.

35
00:04:29,760 --> 00:04:31,220
Fierce fire burns the sky.

36
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:32,770
Fall.

37
00:05:17,080 --> 00:05:17,880
Qingxuan.

38
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:21,140
Are you really going to the mortal world?

39
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:24,000
Leaving the immortal realm,

40
00:05:24,360 --> 00:05:27,560
your 10,000 years of cultivation will be lost,

41
00:05:28,520 --> 00:05:31,040
and everything must start anew.

42
00:05:31,640 --> 00:05:33,170
I was originally a thought,

43
00:05:33,760 --> 00:05:34,880
wandering in chaos

44
00:05:35,360 --> 00:05:36,800
for tens of thousands of years.

45
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:39,000
Later, I was guided by the Heavenly Dao.

46
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:40,159
I have been stationed at Sanshanliu

47
00:05:40,159 --> 00:05:41,200
as a deity

48
00:05:41,760 --> 00:05:43,159
for tens of thousands of years.

49
00:05:43,159 --> 00:05:44,890
Now with confusion in my heart,

50
00:05:45,040 --> 00:05:46,400
I must go to the mortal world

51
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:47,860
to seek the seven emotions

52
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,740
just to find an answer.

53
00:05:51,640 --> 00:05:52,970
I hope the Heavenly Lord

54
00:05:53,600 --> 00:05:54,860
will grant my request.

55
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,080
Your heart is sincere,

56
00:05:58,640 --> 00:05:59,720
and the Heavenly Dao

57
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:01,880
can help you overcome this tribulation.

58
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:04,210
I will leave a trace of your immortal root.

59
00:06:04,640 --> 00:06:06,970
If you encounter demons causing trouble,

60
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:08,160
this sword rainbow

61
00:06:08,520 --> 00:06:10,440
will shine brightly again.

62
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,210
Where the rainbow emerges,

63
00:06:20,760 --> 00:06:23,040
its light shines across the eight directions.

64
00:06:23,040 --> 00:06:24,700
Righteousness fills the air,

65
00:06:24,880 --> 00:06:26,680
and the universe becomes clear.

66
00:06:27,960 --> 00:06:28,760
Keep in mind,

67
00:06:30,680 --> 00:06:32,080
it is your origin.

68
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:35,800
A single thought of god or Buddha can save all beings.

69
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:39,400
A single thought of demonic obsession can disrupt the universe.

70
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:43,040
I hope you can find the answer you seek.

71
00:06:43,600 --> 00:06:44,330
At that time,

72
00:06:44,880 --> 00:06:47,540
you may step into the immortal realm once again.

73
00:07:08,720 --> 00:07:10,320
There's someone over there.

74
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:13,090
Little brother,

75
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:15,860
did you stay here all by yourself last night?

76
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,900
Then you're really lucky.

77
00:07:21,000 --> 00:07:22,160
Hurry up and get out of the mountain.

78
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,080
In this mountain,

79
00:07:23,080 --> 00:07:24,210
there are monsters.

80
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:24,880
Monsters?

81
00:07:26,480 --> 00:07:27,340
What monsters?

82
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:29,570
I really don't know.

83
00:07:29,880 --> 00:07:31,160
I haven't seen them either.

84
00:07:31,160 --> 00:07:33,280
But they have already eaten a lot of people.

85
00:07:33,280 --> 00:07:35,400
It's said they can take human form.

86
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:36,600
It's possible

87
00:07:36,760 --> 00:07:38,040
they're hiding among us.

88
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,320
Is it that mysterious?

89
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,260
You better believe it.

90
00:07:41,360 --> 00:07:43,880
I'm telling you, I saw a pile of bones with my own eyes.

91
00:07:43,880 --> 00:07:46,159
They must be the leftovers of the monsters.

92
00:07:46,159 --> 00:07:47,020
What a tragedy.

93
00:07:48,960 --> 00:07:49,680
Little brother,

94
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:50,360
once you've rested,

95
00:07:50,360 --> 00:07:51,800
hurry out of the mountain.

96
00:07:51,800 --> 00:07:52,800
Let's go.

97
00:08:16,400 --> 00:08:16,860
Master.

98
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,360
Please save our village.

99
00:08:22,520 --> 00:08:22,980
Master.

100
00:08:24,160 --> 00:08:24,620
Master.

101
00:08:24,680 --> 00:08:25,800
You have such great skills.

102
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:27,200
Please save our village.

103
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:29,060
Master.

104
00:08:29,760 --> 00:08:30,960
If you are willing to save our village,

105
00:08:30,960 --> 00:08:32,360
I will agree to anything.

106
00:08:34,280 --> 00:08:34,919
Master.

107
00:08:39,880 --> 00:08:41,080
Why should I help you?

108
00:08:41,280 --> 00:08:42,600
Didn't you defeat the bandits?

109
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,559
You must be a great hero.

110
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:44,480
Since you are a hero,

111
00:08:44,480 --> 00:08:45,940
shouldn't you fight evil?

112
00:08:46,240 --> 00:08:47,040
Fight evil?

113
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,560
What does that have to do with me?

114
00:08:49,560 --> 00:08:51,690
I am just an ordinary medicine seller.

115
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,300
A medicine seller?

116
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,280
What kind of medicine do you sell?

117
00:08:55,280 --> 00:08:56,210
Good luck charms

118
00:08:56,640 --> 00:08:57,770
and wealth pouches.

119
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:58,890
A peace pendant.

120
00:08:59,400 --> 00:09:00,860
An item to pray for safety.

121
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,800
I have everything you need.

122
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,330
Do you want to buy anything?

123
00:09:04,360 --> 00:09:04,820
Master.

124
00:09:04,880 --> 00:09:05,540
Then what do

125
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:06,400
all those talismans you mentioned

126
00:09:06,400 --> 00:09:07,200
have to do with

127
00:09:07,480 --> 00:09:08,340
your medicine?

128
00:09:08,640 --> 00:09:10,760
Medicine isn't the only thing that cures illness.

129
00:09:10,760 --> 00:09:12,290
Anything that saves people

130
00:09:12,400 --> 00:09:13,400
is good medicine.

131
00:09:16,440 --> 00:09:16,880
To me,

132
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:20,800
you don't look like you can afford my goods.

133
00:09:21,040 --> 00:09:21,500
Master.

134
00:09:21,760 --> 00:09:23,090
I may not have money now,

135
00:09:23,240 --> 00:09:23,640
but

136
00:09:23,800 --> 00:09:25,040
if you help us defeat the bandits,

137
00:09:25,040 --> 00:09:26,160
our village will have money.

138
00:09:26,160 --> 00:09:26,680
When that time comes,

139
00:09:26,680 --> 00:09:27,400
I'll buy your goods.

140
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,040
No, no, no.

141
00:09:28,040 --> 00:09:28,840
I mean your medicine.

142
00:09:28,840 --> 00:09:29,570
Is that okay?

143
00:09:30,680 --> 00:09:31,040
No.

144
00:09:32,640 --> 00:09:33,100
Master.

145
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:35,440
If you don't agree to help me today,

146
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:36,840
I'll keep pestering you.

147
00:09:52,080 --> 00:09:52,540
This...

148
00:09:53,080 --> 00:09:54,340
That's not necessary.

149
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:56,500
Master.

150
00:09:56,880 --> 00:09:58,200
Don't go! Let me out!

151
00:09:59,240 --> 00:09:59,760
Master.

152
00:10:01,480 --> 00:10:02,680
Don't leave, Master!

153
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:03,810
Please let me go.

154
00:10:04,560 --> 00:10:05,240
Let me go.

155
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:06,880
Master!

156
00:10:13,480 --> 00:10:14,560
Is the village you mentioned

157
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:15,360
far from here?

158
00:10:15,800 --> 00:10:16,320
Not far.

159
00:10:16,800 --> 00:10:18,280
It's just a few miles ahead.

160
00:10:18,280 --> 00:10:19,140
What happened?

161
00:10:20,240 --> 00:10:21,240
Come back with me,

162
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:22,450
and you'll find out.

163
00:10:26,200 --> 00:10:27,000
Thank you, Master.

164
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:28,060
Thank you, Master.

165
00:10:28,440 --> 00:10:28,970
Release.

166
00:10:37,280 --> 00:10:37,740
Master.

167
00:10:38,680 --> 00:10:39,140
Master.

168
00:10:39,560 --> 00:10:40,560
What is your name?

169
00:10:41,680 --> 00:10:42,140
Master!

170
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:44,040
Why are you always carrying this bag?

171
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:45,600
Why are you always carrying this sword?

172
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:46,080
Master.

173
00:10:46,560 --> 00:10:47,020
Master.

174
00:10:47,080 --> 00:10:47,800
That talisman of yours earlier,

175
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:48,600
how did you do that?

176
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:50,130
How did I go down with a bang?

177
00:10:50,280 --> 00:10:50,740
Shut up.

178
00:10:56,640 --> 00:10:57,480
Chief.

179
00:10:59,680 --> 00:11:00,840
What are you shouting for?

180
00:11:00,840 --> 00:11:01,840
Save your energy.

181
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:02,760
I told you to get some food.

182
00:11:02,760 --> 00:11:03,560
Did you get it?

183
00:11:09,200 --> 00:11:09,960
What happened to you?

184
00:11:09,960 --> 00:11:11,820
Did you just crawl out of the dirt?

185
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,010
I'm fine.

186
00:11:13,400 --> 00:11:14,600
I didn't get any food.

187
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:15,960
But I found a helper.

188
00:11:16,800 --> 00:11:17,530
That master,

189
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:19,160
he just single-handedly

190
00:11:19,160 --> 00:11:20,890
defeated six or seven bandits.

191
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:22,280
Feilu,

192
00:11:23,080 --> 00:11:24,840
are you hallucinating from hunger?

193
00:11:24,840 --> 00:11:25,400
This master,

194
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,600
he's really amazing.

195
00:11:26,680 --> 00:11:28,320
I went to a lot of trouble to invite him over.

196
00:11:28,320 --> 00:11:29,050
Let's beg him

197
00:11:29,240 --> 00:11:30,840
to help us fight the bandits.

198
00:11:32,480 --> 00:11:33,140
Look at him.

199
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:35,940
Does he look like a master?

200
00:11:41,680 --> 00:11:43,540
Look at the people in our village.

201
00:11:44,040 --> 00:11:46,040
They don't even look human anymore.

202
00:11:50,840 --> 00:11:51,440
Forget it.

203
00:11:51,960 --> 00:11:52,760
We just take it

204
00:11:52,840 --> 00:11:53,770
one day at a time.

205
00:11:58,480 --> 00:11:59,560
Oh no! Oh no!

206
00:11:59,560 --> 00:12:01,280
They're here again.

207
00:12:17,800 --> 00:12:19,080
Did you gather

208
00:12:19,640 --> 00:12:20,900
the grain we asked for?

209
00:12:24,200 --> 00:12:24,720
My Lord,

210
00:12:25,200 --> 00:12:26,860
please give us a few more days.

211
00:12:27,440 --> 00:12:28,100
Our village

212
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:28,920
currently has

213
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:30,480
no surplus grain left at all.

214
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:30,960
No?

215
00:12:31,640 --> 00:12:33,080
Then pay with your heads.

216
00:12:33,600 --> 00:12:34,040
Men!

217
00:12:34,680 --> 00:12:36,880
Take away all the women in the village,

218
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:38,480
except those over 60.

219
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:47,040
Haihui.

220
00:13:47,040 --> 00:13:47,400
Jie Qianghai.
